{"TopicId":153368,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Retractable Rover Wheels","CreatedByName":"RentedTritium","CreatedById":172096,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T17:43:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RentedTritium","CreatedById":172096,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T17:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know of a mod with rover wheels that can be retracted? Particularly very large ones, but I would be happy with them in any size. I really want to make a small plane that can drive around once it lands and the key to that is going to be rover wheels that are stowed in a low-drag form on the hull.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf not, can anyone think of an approach I can use to accomplish that using different parts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T18:16:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve use Infernal Robotics to stuff like that, worked pretty well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RentedTritium","CreatedById":172096,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-11T18:35:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh that makes sense. So what you put regular wheels on an assembly that extends out of a bay?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vorg","CreatedById":74652,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-12T00:13:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck roverdudes mods. He has some.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-12T21:43:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe malamute rover from roverdude has some wheels that can be retracted, and I \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ethink\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E the caribou one as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-20T15:08:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172096-rentedtritium/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022172096\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172096-rentedtritium/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RentedTritium\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPBS has two different types. \u003Cem\u003EM\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eaybe\u00A0\u003C/em\u003EB9 but I\u0027m not sure:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/133606-122-kerbal-planetary-base-systems-v1310-20th-december-16/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83570-113-b9-aerospace-release-612-updated-063016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/89874-105-adjustable-landing-gear-v120-masscost-scaling-tech-nodes-drag-may-30/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-23T19:42:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso possible: use the stock landing gear and add the motor segment from a rover wheel to it\u0027s configuration file. 5 minutes work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sharpy","CreatedById":145504,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-26T21:52:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222884253\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153368\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481501618\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274652\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vorg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12.12.2016 at 1:13 AM, Vorg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck roverdudes mods. He has some.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpecifically the Caribou rover mod. While the rover is somewhat lackluster, the retractable ruggedized wheels are awesome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}